<p>The current season premiered last week on the heels of news that Keeping Up With The Kardashians was coming to an end on E! after more than a decade. </p>

<p>Keeping Up With The Kardashians soldiered on for 18 seasons after it first started in 2007 and made superstars out of Kris and all six of her children.</p>

<p>Early last week a Page Six report alleged that Khloe Kardashian and Scott Disick were against the cancellation of the show.</p>

